     <div class="about-header-content no-background"> 
      <h2 class="about-header-title">We’re helping millions of people feel more inspired in their everyday lives. Join us.</h2> 
      <span class="about-header-description"><p><a href="careers/engineering-product"><span class="btn btn-red-big">Current Openings</span></a></p> </span> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
