       <section class="pinterest-panel pinterest-1col-articles clearfix"> 
        <div class="pinterest-panel-region panel-main" role="list"> 
         <div class="panel-pane pane-node-content"> 
          <section class="pinterest-panel pinterest-1col-careers-landing clearfix"> 
           <div class="big-image" style="background-image: url(https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/credo_0.jpg)"> 
            <div class="big-image-mobile" style="background-image: url(https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/m_careersbg_2x.jpg)"></div> 
            <div class="big-image-container"> 
             <div class="field field-name-field-long-text-x5 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"> 
              <p><img class="media-element file-default" src="https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/pinners_first_0.png" alt=""></p> 
              <h3>We put pinners first.</h3> 
              <p>We start by asking, ”Will this product make pinners’ lives better?“<br>We know that if our products don’t work for pinners, they don’t work for us.</p> 
             </div> 
             <div class="field field-name-field-long-text-x5 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"> 
              <p><img class="media-element file-default" src="https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/care_0_0.png" alt=""></p> 
              <h3>We knit.</h3> 
              <p>Innovation happens when disciplines knit.<br>We insist on an open, curious culture<br>where everyone —from engineering and design<br>to marketing to community—works together.</p> 
             </div> 
             <div class="field field-name-field-long-text-x5 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"> 
              <p><img class="media-element file-default" src="https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/ship_0.png" alt=""></p> 
              <h3>We go.</h3> 
              <p>Sometimes the best way to find out<br>if something works is to just go do it.<br>Our process is iterative, and we’re constantly<br>learning from the things we try.</p> 
             </div> 
             <div class="field field-name-field-long-text-x5 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"> 
              <p><img class="media-element file-default" src="https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/authentic.png" alt=""></p> 
              <h3>We’re authentic.</h3> 
              <p>We believe in being warm,<br>honest, open and direct<br>with each other and with pinners.<br>Everything we do should<br>reflect our values.</p> 
             </div> 
             <div class="field field-name-field-long-text-x5 field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"> 
              <p><img class="media-element file-default" src="https://about.pinterest.com/sites/about/files/scale_0.png" alt=""></p> 
              <h3>We scale.</h3> 
              <p>We want Pinterest to be useful for people around the world, however they<br>choose to use it. We’re building our company to make that happen.</p> 
             </div> 
            </div> 
           </div> 
